    "Damstra et al.",
    "compared cephalometric and morphometric MSPs and suggested using a morphometric approach based on intact regions of the skull, unaffected by asymmetry, to determine MSP [15].",
    "Likewise, Hsiao et al.",
    "reported voxel-based morphometric MSP as a more reliable approach compared to the cephalometric method, due to the latter's dependence on the operator's skill in identifying landmarks, whereas the former is less prone to deviation even in cases of severe asymmetry [25].",
